      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WILMA'S OUR GIRL (1) stuck on well last time to finish one length back in second (34.51) at this track in a Grade 5 over 595m. Has a strong record from box 1, including two wins. Likely to feature again. JETSON (2) is a consistent type who is lining up for his first start here. Jumped quickly and was in the firing line throughout when winning last time over 455m at Murray Bridge (25.83). Must be included in calculations. HIJINKERY (4) was strongly fancied but finished second last time (22.90) at Gawler, bringing a three-run winning streak to an end. Won at her only start from this box. Hard to beat again. CLAYMORE LASS (7) scored on debut and can measure up again.",
